title: Friday Sports: General Brown Visits Thousand Islands
text:
16, 2015 at 11:35 PM   17, 2015 at 1:08 AM EDT 
The last football Friday night of the regular season was headlined by a big game in Clayton, undefeated General Brown visiting once beaten Thousand Islands. 
Thousand Islands needed a win to secure a playoff spot.
